could soon change,

00:06:50.600 --> 00:06:52.520 align:middle line:90%
thanks to a famous red brand.

00:06:52.520 --> 00:06:58.760 align:middle line:90%


00:06:58.760 --> 00:06:59.560 align:middle line:90%
>> Let's go.

00:06:59.560 --> 00:07:02.560 align:middle line:90%


00:07:02.560 --> 00:07:04.860 align:middle line:90%
Go on, put on your costume.

00:07:04.860 --> 00:07:10.740 align:middle line:90%
>> [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH]

00:07:10.740 --> 00:07:13.800 align:middle line:84%
>> These 14-year-old
children who participate

00:07:13.800 --> 00:07:17.610 align:middle line:84%
in a competition organized
by Coca-Cola between schools

00:07:17.610 --> 00:07:20.550 align:middle line:84%
of the city, the
school's festival.

00:07:20.550 --> 00:07:24.300 align:middle line:90%
General rehearsal.

00:07:24.300 --> 00:07:30.410 align:middle line:84%
>> The winning school gets
15,000 riyals, that's right.

00:07:30.410 --> 00:07:34.250 align:middle line:90%
And yes, 5,000 riyals--

00:07:34.250 --> 00:07:35.580 align:middle line:90%
that would be great.

00:07:35.580 --> 00:07:40.610 align:middle line:84%
We could buy elastic, footballs,
equipment for volleyball.

00:07:40.610 --> 00:07:43.310 align:middle line:84%
>> Whatever the result, it
will be good for the school.

00:07:43.310 --> 00:07:48.740 align:middle line:90%


00:07:48.740 --> 00:07:51.320 align:middle line:84%
>> This teacher signed
the children up.

00:07:51.320 --> 00:07:54.950 align:middle line:84%
She even has the official
title of brand ambassador--

