00:08:29.230 --> 00:08:31.390 align:middle line:90%
>> 20 bottles maximum.

00:08:31.390 --> 00:08:33.280 align:middle line:90%
>> And Coke?

00:08:33.280 --> 00:08:35.080 align:middle line:90%
>> A lot.

00:08:35.080 --> 00:08:37.480 align:middle line:90%
All the refrigerators.

00:08:37.480 --> 00:08:40.330 align:middle line:90%
>> And how much is that?

00:08:40.330 --> 00:08:45.640 align:middle line:90%
>> About 2,000 cans.

00:08:45.640 --> 00:08:48.490 align:middle line:84%
>> That day, the
brand is everywhere.

00:08:48.490 --> 00:08:50.140 align:middle line:90%
And yet, it's a school event.

00:08:50.140 --> 00:08:54.980 align:middle line:90%


00:08:54.980 --> 00:08:59.050 align:middle line:84%
>> You spend a lot of
money on this operation?

00:08:59.050 --> 00:09:02.540 align:middle line:84%
>> Yes, we've invested a lot
because the goal is to make

00:09:02.540 --> 00:09:05.750 align:middle line:84%
