the best gift that we can give

00:09:05.750 --> 00:09:06.600 align:middle line:90%
them.

00:09:06.600 --> 00:09:11.180 align:middle line:84%
Well, I don't mean children, but
teenagers, from 12 to 19 years

00:09:11.180 --> 00:09:12.365 align:middle line:90%
