00:09:12.365 --> 00:09:20.330 align:middle line:90%


00:09:20.330 --> 00:09:22.255 align:middle line:90%
>> Don't be stressed, breathe.

00:09:22.255 --> 00:09:28.000 align:middle line:90%


00:09:28.000 --> 00:09:31.540 align:middle line:84%
>> It's time for the pupils
