this is marketing?

00:09:54.930 --> 00:09:56.720 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes, well, more or less.

00:09:56.720 --> 00:09:58.630 align:middle line:84%
Because I don't think
Coke needs that.

00:09:58.630 --> 00:10:01.280 align:middle line:90%


