Everybody here knows it.

00:10:09.560 --> 00:10:21.690 align:middle line:90%


00:10:21.690 --> 00:10:22.890 align:middle line:90%
>> Coke forever.

00:10:22.890 --> 00:10:27.360 align:middle line:84%
Today, tomorrow,
Coca-Cola forever.

00:10:27.360 --> 00:10:30.690 align:middle line:84%
The most powerful fizzy
drink brand on the planet

00:10:30.690 --> 00:10:32.670 align:middle line:84%
has guaranteed the
lifelong loyalty

00:10:32.670 --> 00:10:37.520 align:middle line:84%
of these Brazilian
schoolchildren.

00:10:37.520 --> 00:10:39.470 align:middle line:90%
