food from entering

00:11:46.570 --> 00:11:49.300 align:middle line:84%
her school, a daily
battle to protect

00:11:49.300 --> 00:11:51.320 align:middle line:90%
her pupils, aged three to 14.

00:11:51.320 --> 00:11:54.490 align:middle line:90%


00:11:54.490 --> 00:11:58.060 align:middle line:84%
>> In Brazilian canteens, in
general, they serve crisps,

00:11:58.060 --> 00:12:01.210 align:middle line:84%
