00:12:28.450 --> 00:12:30.010 align:middle line:90%
>> Hey, what's up, kids?

00:12:30.010 --> 00:12:32.140 align:middle line:90%
Everything going OK?

00:12:32.140 --> 00:12:33.310 align:middle line:90%
