Wow, what an honor.

00:12:36.790 --> 00:12:40.510 align:middle line:84%
>> We pass ourselves
off as pupils' parents.

00:12:40.510 --> 00:12:41.450 align:middle line:90%
>> Hello.

00:12:41.450 --> 00:12:44.020 align:middle line:90%
>> Hello.

00:12:44.020 --> 00:12:46.210 align:middle line:84%
>> Here we go,
everybody is here.

